<section name="333">
	<p>You are on the east bank of the River Grimm. <random type="travel" dice="1"/>.</p>
	<outcomes>
		<outcome range="1,2">
			A water sprite curses you - <lose blessing="?">lose a Blessing</lose>, if you have one
		</outcome>
		<outcome range="3,4">Nothing happens</outcome>
		<outcome range="5,6">
			Catch a <item name="smoulder fish"/> while fishing
		</outcome>
	</outcomes>
	<p>When you are ready, you can:</p>
	<choices>
		<choice book="2" section="99">Cross to the west bank</choice>
		<choice section="47">Head east into the Forest of Larun</choice>
		<choice section="123">Follow the river north</choice>
		<choice section="99">Follow the river south</choice>
	</choices>
</section>
